[[!meta title="Dragon Avenger"]]
[[!tag books books/fantasy]]

The second dragon book from E. E. Knight.  Auron's sister Wistala,
whom he considered to be less capable, and who, in his opinion, had to
be protected, turns out to have not died, and indeed, gone to greater
lengths than her brother.  This is a better set of books than the
vampire Earth set.

